><p><strong><span color="rgba(230, 0, 38, 1)" fontSize="12" fontFamily="思源黑体">⚠️ 现状：移动端研发资源及安全研发资源空白</span></strong></p></content></shape><shape width="250" height="45" topLeftX="69.64705882352939" topLeftY="447.7125713634924" type="text" id="bbR"><content fontSize="11" fontFamily="思源黑体" color="rgba(75, 85, 99, 1)" lineSpacing="multiple:1.2"><p lineSpacing="multiple:1.2"><span color="rgba(75, 85, 99, 1)" fontSize="11" fontFamily="思源黑体">团队目前无专职 APP 开发人员，现有跨端方案无法满足复杂交互与性能需求，安全技术支撑存在结构性缺口。</span></p></content></shape><line id="bwo" startX="329.64705882352945" startY="417.7125713634924" endX="329.64705882352945" endY="492.7192377338891"><border color="rgba(230, 0, 38, 0.2)" width="1"/></line><shape width="250" height="24" topLeftX="344.6470588235294" topLeftY="417.7125713634924" type="text" id="bwU"><content fontSize="12" fontFamily="思源黑体" color="rgba(230, 0, 38, 1)" bold="true"><p><strong><span color="rgba(230, 0, 38, 1)" fontSize="12" fontFamily="思源黑体">🚧 影响：直接阻塞商业化闭环</span></strong></p></content></shape><shape width="250" height="45" topLeftX="344.6470588235294" topLeftY="447.7125713634924" type="text" id="bbD"><content fontSize="11" fontFamily="思源黑体" color="rgba(75, 85, 99, 1)" lineSpacing="multiple:1.2"><p lineSpacing="multiple:1.2"><span color="rgba(75, 85, 99, 1)" fontSize="11" fontFamily="思源黑体">下半年“订阅体系”与“生态拓展”高度依赖移动端入口，缺失将导致核心商业功能延期，错失市场窗口期。</span></p></content></shape><line id="bbH" startX="604.6470588235294" startY="417.7125713634924" endX="604.6470588235294" endY="492.7192377338891"><border color="rgba(230, 0, 38, 0.2)" width="1"/></line><shape width="250" height="24" topLeftX="619.6470588235294" topLeftY="417.7125713634924" type="text" id="bwb"><content fontSize="15" fontFamily="思源黑体" color="rgba(230, 0, 38, 1)" bold="true"><p><strong><span color="rgba(230, 0, 38, 1)" fontSize="15" fontFamily="思源黑体">✅ 诉求：紧急增补 2 名 HC</span></strong></p></content></shape><shape width="250" height="45" topLeftX="619.6470588235294" topLeftY="447.7125713634924" type="text" id="bwt"><content fontSize="11" fontFamily="思源黑体" color="rgba(75, 85, 99, 1)" lineSpacing="multiple:1.2"><p lineSpacing="multiple:1.2"><span color="rgba(75, 85, 99, 1)" fontSize="11" fontFamily="思源黑体">亟需招聘一名资深 APP 开发工程师和一名安全工程师，补齐移动端研发/安全研发短板，确保 H2 战略目标如期达成，避免业务停滞。</span></p></content></shape></data><note id="bbL"><content/></note></slide>